      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-09-20T13:32:41Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Retirement Investments for a Sustainable Economy Act of 2018 or the RISE Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a new fund&#8212;the Climate Choice Stock Index Fund&#8212;as an investment option under the Thrift Savings Plan.</p> <p>The Climate Choice Stock Index Fund must be invested in a portfolio that is designed to replicate the performance of a commonly recognized index comprised of common stock and to ensure that no investment in the portfolio is an investment in a fossil fuel entity. </p>]]></text>
